<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure — Science Solved It"
  description="Transparency about how we earn commissions and maintain editorial independence."
  breadcrumbs={[
    { name: 'Home', url: '/' },
    { name: 'Affiliate Disclosure', url: '/affiliate-disclosure/' }
  ]}
>
  <div class="container-narrow" style="padding:3rem 0">
    <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>

    <p>Science Solved It is committed to full transparency about how we make money.</p>

    <h2>How We Earn</h2>
    <p>
      We participate in affiliate programs including Impact.com, Awin, CJ Affiliate, and Amazon Associates. 
      When you click an affiliate link on our site and make a purchase, we earn a commission at no extra cost to you.
    </p>

    <h2>Editorial Independence</h2>
    <p>
      Affiliate relationships do not influence our reviews, ratings, or recommendations. 
      Every product is tested and evaluated using the same objective criteria regardless of whether it has an affiliate program.
    </p>
    <p>
      If a product performs poorly, we say so — even if it means losing a commission.
    </p>

    <h2>Identifying Affiliate Links</h2>
    <p>
      Affiliate links are clearly marked with a disclosure notice at the top of each review, guide, or comparison.
    </p>

    <h2>Questions?</h2>
    <p>Email us at <a href="mailto:hello@sciencesolvedit.store">hello@sciencesolvedit.store</a>.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
